  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a tava-griddle over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and ginger, and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken breast and cook until browned on all sides, about 5-7 minutes.",
    "Add the curry powder, cumin, salt, and pepper, and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the dashi extract, pine nuts, and cilantro, and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the lemon juice and water, and bring to a simmer.",
    "Cook for 10-15 minutes, or until the chicken is cooked through and the liquid has thickened slightly."
